Race.SpecificTitle: Recreation District No. 8 -- 9.96 Mills - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall Recreation District No. 8 of the Parish of Lafourche, State of Louisiana (the "District"), levy a nine and ninety-six hundredths (9.96) mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $65,548 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year) for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2020 and ending with the year 2029, for the purpose of constructing, acquiring, improving, maintaining and operating recreational facilities for the District?
